{"tid":395482,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【打到變植物人】獨家現場片 兇手輕判 受害者家屬喊不公","createTime":"2017-09-10T22:25:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-11T03:00:01.000Z","uid":43510,"like":1,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c273ca09c2b7a468bc26a11c8eac7cd27ce14163","tid":395482,"uid":43510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T22:25:48.000Z","msg":"你就打到人下半生躺在床上，就如醫生所說比死更慘，你只判二十二個月。」阿桐的父親去年因為泊車問題，被一名貨車司機毆打變成植物人，被告早前只被判監二十二個月，阿桐覺得判刑實在太輕，未能反映事件的嚴重性。 <br />\n<br />\n去年十月十八日，阿桐父親關德華（64歲），於旺角弼街泊車，遭前方貨車司機馬海權（39歲）指摘泊得太貼，阻礙他上貨。雙方為此爭吵，其後貨車司機出拳襲擊關，昏迷地上後仍繼續打。 <br />\n<br />\n對於當日情況，阿桐仍歷歷在目，「突然樓下有一名女士，衝上來說：『關小姐，關先生被人打，關先生被人打呀，你快些下去看看。」阿桐跟母親趕到落樓，父親已被人打至奄奄一息，「當時我抱著父親，他已經沒有反應，雙眼反白，之後更開始嘔血。」 <br />\n<br />\n目擊的街坊向阿桐表示，兩人是因為泊車問題爭執，貨車司機更發狂似的毆打其父親，「是被告先動手，我父親只是用手擋架，之後被告仍繼續打，然後父親暈在地上，完全失去意識，他仍然打我父親。被告的同事已拉著他，但他仍照打，還要打頭部，所以父親的頭骨全碎了。」 <br />\n<br />\n而阿桐向本刊提供了一段短片，顯示當日事發後，她與母親趕抵現場，母親不斷追問被告為何要打人，而被告全程聲大夾惡，更誣蔑是受害人先打他。 <br />\n<br />\n父親入院至今一直昏迷，現於廣華醫院留醫，「他九成會是植物人，基本上九成已肯定，就算他一成機會醒過來，他也會嚴重傷殘，會盲，會聽不到。因為他這邊腦部被嚴重擊打。其實(他的情況)是很慘，醫生甚至說比死更慘。」 <br />\n<br />\n【打到變植物人】受害人女兒：直頭想殺人啦 <br />\n( <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2gQuA1e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2gQuA1e&d=3xCMysoeWQKAvrXOxL%2FWiU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=0e44c58c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2gQuA1e</a> ) <br />\n<br />\n上月中，被告在區域法院被判傷人罪成，並不是較嚴重的蓄意傷人罪，被判入獄二十二個月，阿桐一家都覺得判刑太輕，對她父親不公平，「是沒可能，二十二個月，令他人下半生這樣子，很不公平，很不公平。」 <br />\n<br />\n他們亦覺得，被告對事件亦沒有悔意，「他（被告）聽判決那刻還笑的，很輕鬆地笑，我覺得他完全沒反省的想法。只判二十二個月，坐完二十二個月出來，他就沒事了，但我父親就繼續躺在床上，以後就這樣躺在床上。」"},{"pid":"7c8858a1a23dbf5b62203f5a611743745eb69bde","tid":395482,"uid":5650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T22:36:38.000Z","msg":"下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁樣直頭謀殺啦下嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a6d8a6134f07b685246d6fedb7de71eff0a2a09","tid":395482,"uid":43510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T22:44:58.000Z","msg":"有冇人知道之前奶糖羹打死人要坐幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e226250e4b5f5cb0eb84016037bfa2e01516902","tid":395482,"uid":15993,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T22:45:17.000Z","msg":"香港司法真係一個笑話"},{"pid":"fdfca14e642316063c018b3315fcc6db241311df","tid":395482,"uid":13856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T23:10:22.000Z","msg":"被告在區域法院被判傷人罪成，並不是較嚴重的蓄意傷人罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa8f7c62daadbf0b33c18f07719b4b118b51eb4","tid":395482,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T23:16:59.000Z","msg":"意圖謀殺啦"},{"pid":"fdfef38a2dcabfe142d472d8c4cbb7fd9f366d02","tid":395482,"uid":11447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T23:17:06.000Z","msg":"貨車撚以為上落貨大撚曬"},{"pid":"4888c4edd015997ec526038936153df34c08ec88","tid":395482,"uid":38948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T23:17:18.000Z","msg":"企圖謀殺都判咁細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a464ce0d875a599781a32ef0da502b08eff115df","tid":395482,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T23:18:00.000Z","msg":"判刑事撚旦旦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e61e23b7cbc85b11831f80d24a8dc481200a917c","tid":395482,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T23:18:30.000Z","msg":"人地暈左就停手啦"},{"pid":"c51b2af8569cf177bcca42f219c55866e287b2ce","tid":395482,"uid":118131,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T23:22:18.000Z","msg":"09 年既新聞? 不過好恐怖"},{"pid":"ba648addc8518f73a94f5be40a2ae8a2b4ac3a0d","tid":395482,"uid":64548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T23:25:47.000Z","msg":"上訴啦"},{"pid":"f91d6c3a24a8ab42b56775932a609c213444fbfe","tid":395482,"uid":10242,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T23:33:14.000Z","msg":"我覺得廢老抵死<br />\n有揸過車都知阻到人 <br />\n人地都會客氣同你講可唔可以前少少 <br />\n其實佢泊前少少 咪唔洗比人打"},{"pid":"513f07ef76c196a438838cfd6a97e882761627ad","tid":395482,"uid":48286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T23:37:19.000Z","msg":"見到死者個女個樣<br />\n連登仔就會好激動"},{"pid":"50c8ccc140e2061c845f358d6bec1dc387a465b7","tid":395482,"uid":23763,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T23:46:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到死者個女個樣<br />\n連登仔就會好激動</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n要判死刑！"},{"pid":"c6ba9e997e5fe3063c7c49c4d4b7310d0c35603e","tid":395482,"uid":87511,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T23:47:30.000Z","msg":"首先我唔係想合理化個貨車司機個行為<br />\n佢絕對係罪有應得<br />\n<br />\n不過其實個司機並唔係佢屋企人講到咁無辜<br />\n係自己衝落車講嘢得罪人在先<br />\n個貨車佬本身上緊貨,都讓佢架車走先<br />\n但係佢仲落車屌鳩個貨車佬阻到佢<br />\n<br />\n利申 <br />\n當時喺附近返工返咗幾個月,見過個貨車佬好多次 <br />\n如果平時佢上貨阻到人<br />\n你同佢講聲,佢都會100%即刻讓"},{"pid":"badeb1422e55a8368233d433139617089c5215cb","tid":395482,"uid":49542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T23:48:04.000Z","msg":"痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f9e1673b0c81464bff63737a20059a38023657","tid":395482,"uid":67237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T23:54:39.000Z","msg":"要求上訴"},{"pid":"e40f208096e82b47264867b44b9526f0e3c4a724","tid":395482,"uid":68661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T23:57:42.000Z","msg":"留名睇貨車佬講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔跟咁貼住"},{"pid":"773f4ddce1a59e4670963fe27f95605c2d8cfebc","tid":395482,"uid":82262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T23:59:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人知道之前奶糖羹打死人要坐幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果單死左人"},{"pid":"0afa67d232a9c6197b5b912e6b0a6dcb5e273afb","tid":395482,"uid":10242,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T23:59:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>首先我唔係想合理化個貨車司機個行為<br />\n佢絕對係罪有應得<br />\n<br />\n不過其實個司機並唔係佢屋企人講到咁無辜<br />\n係自己衝落車講嘢得罪人在先<br />\n個貨車佬本身上緊貨,都讓佢架車走先<br />\n但係佢仲落車屌鳩個貨車佬阻到佢<br />\n<br />\n利申 <br />\n當時喺附近返工返咗幾個月,見過個貨車佬好多次 <br />\n如果平時佢上貨阻到人<br />\n你同佢講聲,佢都會100%即刻讓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我再講多個我親眼見既 <br />\n有次係西貢勝記果邊食飯 <br />\n啲車泊到出公廁<br />\n等車位 有架貨車等緊貨車位 <br />\n跟住有架寶馬隊左落貨車位 <br />\n貨車司機都好客氣咁同佢講<br />\n阿師兄 而個貨車位黎 <br />\n寶馬：咁又點 <br />\n貨車佬：而個位比人落貨用 <br />\n寶馬：死撚開啦咕哩 <br />\n<br />\n貨車佬即刻閘住佢 用擴音報警 <br />\n之後寶馬想走都走唔到 <br />\n兩個企到好埋 差啲打<br />\n但佢兩個跟車一落車 寶馬佬又縮沙<br />\n之後警察黎到 抄哂成個場啲牌<br />\n我諗無40都有30架車係到"},{"pid":"4e35bbb22539aaefdd17dde0811bd61c9d315096","tid":395482,"uid":33545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T00:08:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇人知道之前奶糖羹打死人要坐幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果單死左人</blockquote><br />\n唔知告謀殺定誤殺呢？"},{"pid":"17405594861082f3e91de0ade03d259dac7371b3","tid":395482,"uid":75524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T00:24:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>首先我唔係想合理化個貨車司機個行為<br />\n佢絕對係罪有應得<br />\n<br />\n不過其實個司機並唔係佢屋企人講到咁無辜<br />\n係自己衝落車講嘢得罪人在先<br />\n個貨車佬本身上緊貨,都讓佢架車走先<br />\n但係佢仲落車屌鳩個貨車佬阻到佢<br />\n<br />\n利申 <br />\n當時喺附近返工返咗幾個月,見過個貨車佬好多次 <br />\n如果平時佢上貨阻到人<br />\n你同佢講聲,佢都會100%即刻讓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我再講多個我親眼見既 <br />\n有次係西貢勝記果邊食飯 <br />\n啲車泊到出公廁<br />\n等車位 有架貨車等緊貨車位 <br />\n跟住有架寶馬隊左落貨車位 <br />\n貨車司機都好客氣咁同佢講<br />\n阿師兄 而個貨車位黎 <br />\n寶馬：咁又點 <br />\n貨車佬：而個位比人落貨用 <br />\n寶馬：死撚開啦咕哩 <br />\n<br />\n貨車佬即刻閘住佢 用擴音報警 <br />\n之後寶馬想走都走唔到 <br />\n兩個企到好埋 差啲打<br />\n但佢兩個跟車一落車 寶馬佬又縮沙<br />\n之後警察黎到 抄哂成個場啲牌<br />\n我諗無40都有30架車係到</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bd1c00de0b0f1fd9da069d7ba78b3ef51f8f65d","tid":395482,"uid":35581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T00:49:11.000Z","msg":"係香港 仲信司法制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n政治犯就重判 殺人放火輕判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a16f73ecc41732d6f0f7269350720e375f9e44","tid":395482,"uid":71703,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T01:44:44.000Z","msg":"痴線 22個月<br />\n貨車司機正一垃圾"}]}